event.logging

Class AuthenticateEventAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • event.logging.AuthenticateEventAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventAction, HasOutcome

    public class AuthenticateEventAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements EventAction, HasOutcome
    Used to record authentication events such as logon and logoff. All authentication events that originate from a client device should record details of the client device in the event source.

    Java class for Authenticate complex type.

    The following schema fragment specifies the expected content contained within this class.
